  "prompt": "From which institute should I learn post production and lightning, sound camera etc for my YouTube channel in Delhi?",
  "response": "In Delhi, there are several reputable institutes that offer courses in post-production, lighting, sound, and camera techniques that would be beneficial for enhancing your skills for your YouTube channel. Here are some options you can consider:\n\n1. **Film and Television Institute of India (FTII) - Delhi Centre**: This institute is known for its comprehensive courses in film and television production, including post-production and cinematography.\n\n2. **Asian Academy of Film and Television (AAFT)**: Located in Noida (close to Delhi), AAFT offers various courses in filmmaking, post-production, and multimedia that could be useful for your needs.\n\n3. **National Institute of Fashion Technology (NIFT)**: NIFT offers courses related to media studies that include aspects of film and video production.\n\n4. **Whistling Woods International**: Though primarily based in Mumbai, they have online courses and workshops that cover various aspects of film and media production, including sound and lighting.\n\n5. **Delhi Film Institute**: They offer specialized courses in film production, including practical training in camera work, lighting, and sound.\n\n6. **Red Digital Cinema**: Offers workshops and training sessions on various aspects of cinematography and digital filmmaking.\n\n7. **Anupam Kher's Actor Prepares**: While primarily an acting school, they also conduct workshops focused on filmmaking and production techniques.\n\nConsider checking their websites or contacting them directly for detailed information on the courses they offer, duration, fees, and how they align with your specific needs for your YouTube channel. Additionally, local community centers or workshops may offer short-term courses that might also be beneficial.",
